2. Write a program to calculate CGPA using marks of three subject (on the scale of 10)    
3. Write Java program which asks the user to enter his/her name and greets them with "Hello <name> , have a good day" text
4. Write a Java program to convert kilometers to miles {Hint : 1 Miles = KM * 0.621371}
5. Write a Java program to detect whether a number entered by the user is integer or not
