ðŸ‘‰ CODE 1 : 

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args){
        int num1 = 34;
        int num2 = 35;
        int num3 = 36;
        int sum  = num1+num2+num3;
        System.out.println(sum);
    }
}

ðŸ‘‰ Output : 105
