ðŸ‘‰ CODE 5 : 

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main{
    public static void main(String[] args){
        System.out.println("Enter the Number : ");
        Scanner sc= new Scanner(System.in);
        boolean isInt = sc.hasNextInt();
        System.out.println("If you entered the integer then value is True otherwise False : "+ isInt);
    }
}

ðŸ‘‰ Output : 

Enter the Number : 
45
If you entered the integer then value is True otherwise False : true

Enter the Number : 
46.5
If you entered the integer then value is True otherwise False : false

